softs scheduled monthly security update release.'),(154,'Adware primarily:','Shows unwanted ads','Deletes files','Encrypts drives','Steals hardware','A','Intermediate','Level_3','Malware','Adware displays intrusive or unwanted ads.'),(155,'Full Disk Encryption protects:','Wallpapers','Stored data if device stolen','Wi-Fi speed','Charging port','B','Intermediate','Level_3','Locking Devices','Disk encryption protects stored data if devices are stolen.'),(156,'Next-Generation Firewalls (NGFW) include:','DPI & intrusion prevention','Cooling fans','Storage drives','BIOS updates','A','Intermediate','Level_3','Firewall','NGFWs include deep packet inspection and intrusion prevention.'),(157,'Official updates should be downloaded from:','Ads','Third-party sites','Official vendor website/app store','Emails','C','Intermediate','Level_3','Software Updates','Updates should only come from official sources.'),(158,'Rootkits target:','Application layer','Deep system/OS control','Only browsers','Printers','B','Intermediate','Level_3','Malware','Rootkits gain deep system control and hide from detection.'),(159,'SIM lock PIN protects:','Phone battery','SIM misuse','Wi-Fi access','Bluetooth','B','Intermediate','Level_3','Locking Devices','SIM PIN prevents SIM misuse in stolen phones.'),(160,'DPI stands for:','Deep Packet Inspection','Data Protocol Interface','Digital Packet Index','Dual Packet Internet','A','Intermediate','Level_3','Firewall','DPI means Deep Packet Inspection.'),(161,'Firewall rules define:','Allowed & blocked traffic','Screen brightness','CPU load','Storage usage','A','Intermediate','Level_4','Firewall','Firewall rules determine allowed and blocked traffic.'),(162,'Outdated software is vulnerable to:','Faster speed','Exploits','UI bugs only','Hardware damage','B','Intermediate','Level_4','Software Updates','Outdated software is vulnerable to exploits.'),(163,'Remote lock feature allows:','Locking device via internet','Charging remotely','Tracking Wi-Fi','Updating OS',